{{main|1912年牙买加飓风}}
{{lang|en|UTC}}11月11日早上6点，西南[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的低气压区已发展成热带风暴<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="Meta" />。气旋起初缓慢向西北移动，之后又蜿蜒向东北偏北前进，船只观测报告表明风暴于11月13日晚增强成飓风<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="Meta" />。接下来气旋继续缓慢强化，但转向东北移动后增强速度加快。11月17日清晨，风暴达到最大持续风速每小时185公里的最高强度，再继续向东北偏北移动，于{{lang|en|UTC}}11月18日中午12点左右从[[牙买加|牙买加]][[内格里尔|内格里尔]]附近登陆。南内格里尔角（{{lang|en|South Negril Point}}）测得965毫巴（百帕，28.5英寸汞柱）气压值，<ref name="Meta" />这也是文献记载中本场风暴的最低气压。飓风登陆后迅速减弱，并且回到加勒比海后仍在继续快速弱化。11月20日，气旋在[[古巴|古巴]]以南洋面减弱成热带风暴，接下来向西穿越加勒比海，最终于11月22日在[[大开曼|大开曼]]西南方向约185公里洋面逐渐消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。

牙买加降下暴雨，该岛北部和东部多座桥梁严重受损<ref name="JamaicaReport">{{cite journal | title = The Storms Of November In Jamaica, West Indies | journal = Monthly Weather Review | date = 1912-11 | volume = 40 | pages = 1756–1757 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115203/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/040/mwr-040-11-1756b.pdf | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1912)40<1756b:TSONIJ>2.0.CO;2 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/040/mwr-040-11-1756b.pdf | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | publisher = American Meteorological Society | format = PDF | deadurl = no | bibcode = 1912MWRv...40R1756. | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。飓风产生的狂风将约四分之一的香蕉树摧毁<ref name="UnprecedentedRains">{{cite news | title = Unprecedented Rains Hurt Jamaican Fruits | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 101 | issue = 126 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850519/1912_jamaica_hurricane/? | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | newspaper = San Francisco Chronicle | date = 1912-11-17 | location = San Francisco, California | archive-date = 2019-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190612002949/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850519/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>，多地电报线路中断，铁轨也受到狂风暴雨的沉重打击<ref name="StormContinues">{{cite news | title = Jamaican Storm Continues | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850390/1912_jamaican_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | newspaper = The Parsons Daily Sun | date = 1912-11-18 | location = Parsons, Kansas | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 32 | issue = 325 | archive-date = 2019-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190606112407/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850390/1912_jamaican_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。岛屿周边海域波涛汹涌，[[滨海萨凡纳|滨海萨凡纳]]几乎被完全摧毁，有42人丧生。牙买加西部约有100幢民宅被毁，5000套建筑受损或毁于一旦。<ref name="EntireTown">{{cite news | title = Entire Town Wiped Out | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850669/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | newspaper = The Daily Northwestern | date = 1912-11-20 | location = Oshkosh, Wisconsin | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | agency = Associated Press | archive-date = 2016-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821062716/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850669/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>整个牙买加约有100人遇难，损失数额约150万美元<ref name="JamaicaReport" />。此外，气旋还在古巴[[关塔那摩湾|关塔那摩湾]]区域引发大面积洪灾，共夺走五条人命<ref name="ency">{{cite book | author = David Longshore | title = Encyclopedia of Hurricanes, Typhoons, and Cyclones, New Edition | page = 55-56 | location = New York | publisher = Facts on File | date = 2010-05-12 | accessdate = 2016-12-26 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8kXwskQHBLoC&pg=PA56&lpg=PA56&dq=black+river+hurricane&source=bl&ots=qEJf5N9d-S&sig=3VRpXyvKHrEYPH17dwGF5d7Q3WI&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjw8YyGw4zNAhXBqh4KHc-BAQEQ6AEISjAL#v=onepage&q=black%20river%20hurricane&f=false}}</ref>。
